OL,3,CPast 'failures' is why Birmingham City
OL,4,CCouncil finances are a 'mess'
OL,6,FBirmingham City Council is planning to
OL,7,Fhike council tax and make cuts to
OL,8,Flocal services for the second year in
OL,9,Fa row.
OL,11,FThe proposed budget was discussed by
OL,12,Fcabinet members at a meeting on
OL,13,FTuesday 11 February, during which the
OL,14,FLabour council faced heavy criticism
OL,15,Ffrom opposition councillors.
OL,17,FWhat are the cuts being proposed in
OL,18,Fthe current budget?
OL,20,FWhy is Birmingham City Council in such
OL,21,Ffinancial distress?
