OL,3,CPast 'failures' is why Birmingham City
OL,4,CCouncil finances are a 'mess'
OL,6,FCllr Roger Harmer, leader of the
OL,7,FLiberal Democrats at the council,
OL,8,Fargued the council's past "failures"
OL,9,Fwere a "massive element of the reason
OL,10,Fwe are in this mess".
OL,12,FIn particular, he pointed to headline
OL,13,Fissues around equal pay, the
OL,14,Fimplementation of the Oracle system
OL,15,Fand the Perry Barr saga, which caused
OL,16,Fa significant financial loss for the
OL,17,Fcouncil.
