OL,3,CPast 'failures' is why Birmingham City
OL,4,CCouncil finances are a 'mess'
OL,6,F"Until we really get to grips with
OL,7,Fsome of the reasons for that
OL,8,Fhappening, we are at risk of further
OL,9,Fthings going wrong," Cllr Harmer
OL,10,Fwarned.
OL,12,FCllr John Cotton, leader of the
OL,13,Fcouncil, was among the Labour cabinet
OL,14,Fmembers who pointed out the "wider
OL,15,Fcontext" that's affecting councils
OL,16,Facross the country.
