OL,3,CPast 'failures' is why Birmingham City
OL,4,CCouncil finances are a 'mess'
OL,6,FBirmingham is not the only council
OL,7,Ffacing equal pay claims. Many such
OL,8,Fauthorities are struggling with issues
OL,9,Fsuch as budget gaps and the rising
OL,10,Fdemand for services.
OL,12,FHe went on to say there has never been
OL,13,Fany "stepping back from taking
OL,14,Fresponsibility" when it came to
OL,15,FBirmingham-specific issues.
OL,17,FCllr Cotton adds: "There's stuff for
OL,18,Fwhich we are responsible that we are
OL,19,Fdoing our part to put right," he said.
OL,20,F"It's exactly what this budget and
OL,21,F(the recovery plan) is about.
