OL,6,F"Nobody is in denial"
OL,8,FCllr Robert Alden, leader of the
OL,9,FConservatives at the council,
OL,10,Fmeanwhile highlighted comments from
OL,11,Fgovernment-appointed commissioners,
OL,12,Fwho suggested the council has not done
OL,13,Fenough to maximise "efficiencies and
OL,14,Ftransformation savings".
OL,16,F"The more that is being done through
OL,17,Ftransforming the way the council
OL,18,Foperates, the more that frontline
OL,19,Fservices can actually be protected,"
OL,20,Fhe said.
