OL,6,FCllr Sharon Thompson, deputy leader at
OL,7,Fthe council, responded to such
OL,8,Fconcerns by saying: "Nobody is in
OL,9,Fdenial of the scale of the challenges
OL,10,Fthat we face when it comes to the
OL,11,Ffinances and the work we need to do in
OL,12,Fterms of modernising the council.
OL,14,F"There's absolute commitment there
OL,15,Ffrom the cabinet."
