OL,6,FPlans for a raft of cuts to local
OL,7,Fservices and a council tax hike of
OL,8,Faround 7.5 per cent are now set to be
OL,9,Fvoted on at a full council meeting on
OL,10,FFebruary 25 after being considered by
OL,11,Fcabinet members on Tuesday.
